Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.44,0:00:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if you brought them over?\NSo what if you have Drifters?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many of those\Nidiots you transport here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.61,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Black King Occupies Northern Fortress"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they won't stand a chance against my Ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.37,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Black King Occupies Northern Fortress"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know I'll be the victor?\NDon't waste your time fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just meekly admit your defeat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:36.01,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Closed"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murasaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:41.93,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 4\NActive Heart"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who, like yourselves,\Nare transported from other worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are called "Drifters."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, those who, like Drifters, \Nare brought to this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but are inhuman and evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are called the "Ends."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goals as the Octobrists\Nare to evaluate, monitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and unite those Drifters\Nto stand against the Ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.38,0:01:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Errr... can you untie me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I have no clue\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olminu from the Octobrist Organization,\Nyou totally misjudged me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the powerful Demon King\Nof the Sixth Heaven. Good... Evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who dares judge what I am?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be the absolute evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:42.62,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mutter mutter mutter"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. As might be expected from a\Nformer hipster, you're thick-skinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, which one are we supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you are of the Ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are transported\Nas the Ends are inhuman...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and don't understand such jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They nourish a deep, deep loathing\Ntowards this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened to them\Nwhile they were in your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they detest everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which drives their ambition\Nfor the annihilation of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They only have one objective \Nin mind, which is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the eradication and \Nslaughter of all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They gathered in the north, pacified the\Nmonsters in order to ally with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and began advancing into our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we let them continue,\Nthe world will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm asking you Drifters for help!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about\Nmonsters or those sorts of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the enemy was an organized force, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.15,0:03:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do the Octobrists\Nhave to stand against them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is... umm...\NWe are a magician organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission is to bring Drifters together--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.75,0:03:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you have nothing, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... We call for military support\Nfrom kings and feudal lords,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and assigning Drifters to\Ncommand of these troops is our...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid, stupid, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiefs clearly work the \Nsame way in every world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A feudal lord wields military power.\NThat is how feudalism works.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No lord would ever willingly cede command\Nto some random outsider, stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of how powerful\Nthose so-called Ends are,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a feudal lord will never hand over\Nhis military authority to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if these "apocalyptic forces"\Nare marching into his last stronghold,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they drive him into a corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will persevere until the time\Nof his honorable suicide, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what an overlord is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can theorize as much as you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the end, things are as they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why Mohism was destroyed\Nduring the Warring States Era in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man... Is this the true Oda Nobunaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he just a fool, or is he the Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then, what should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Drifters can defeat them!\NWhat are you suggesting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Drifters should take \Ncontrol of the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby declare that we're
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beginning a campaign of conquest \Nwith Toyohisa as our leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you people will support us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aid our plot to take down the empire
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the sake of your world's\Npeace and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I the leader?!\NYou've never told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Don't you remember you sat\Nin the center the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.43,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to sit down,\Nbut I'll let you take my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can be truly dense, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grrr, shut up! Just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gr-Grand Master, this is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys are behaving \Ncompletely erratically.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, their idea has a certain appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were attacked by the Ends\Nseveral times in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time, they decimated our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, this time is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ill-conceived measures won't work.\NWe'll be totally destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by that Black King!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:06:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Majesty, we completely demolished\Nthe Northern Wall in Carneades.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about our losses, Rasputin?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number of casualties is \N274 in Goblin special forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,345 in Kobold advanced guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...plus four Dragner aerial cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The damage was not serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but losing four Dragners was a heavy blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me those who were injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you truly act, Black Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goblins, Kobolds, and Dragons\Nare all my brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save as many as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are merciful, Black Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch... Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done. You fought hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inform everybody of the fall\Nof the "Northern Wall."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, those who feared humans
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.51,0:07:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and didn't believe the human\Nworld would come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will fill our ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to save humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they rejected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I have no choice but to\Nsave demihumans and destroy humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is terrifying, Black Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go after the escaped Drifters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search... Search...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find out where those\Nmagicians dropped them off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and where they will be sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them unite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No enemy but the Drifters exists before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave no stone unturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find them. Chase them. Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll side with the one \Nthat interests me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am inexorable...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Inexorable Tribulation\Nwho wanders and bellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eradication of mankind \Nwon't be over until...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the annihilation of every\Nsingle human is complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the salvation of every\Nsingle demihuman is at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die on me, you piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull up... you fuckin' jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, this hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!\NYou wanna try me, bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late to talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We killed the lord's knight.\NThere is no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those Drifters...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lord is not going to\Nlisten to such excuses, is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, more than half of the\Nwheat field was burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not enough left\Nto pay the tax to the lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the lord forgives us,\Nhe will confiscate the whole harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be unable to feed the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The punitive forces are\Napproaching the village as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't act now, we'll end up being
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,killed or dying from hunger, guaranteed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We can't take this any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to overthrow the lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be foolish! We don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yea, do, yea, do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yea, do. Yea, do. You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,win chance, yea, yea, do. \NYou rebel. That so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Nobu Nobu, Yoicchii, Toyo Toyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:10:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey! What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--all have power power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. They have no idea\Nwhat he's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:11.98,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mutter mutter mutter"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Here he goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you speak our language?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... We are a magician organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, we've been \Ninvestigating you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Master created this convenient charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Applying it grants you instant fluency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't our Grand Master great?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd known such a \Nconvenient thing existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Do you know how hard it was\Nfor Yoichi to learn their language?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to Yoichi. Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just apologize to him.\NDon't you feel sympathy for him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.01,0:11:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'm sorry... So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over that charm to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... please wait for a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a Far Eastern samurai-looking person...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... this might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon. Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon... Good afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! He looks like a weird zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about where you \Nput those things, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These resemble the charms created\Nby the Onmyodo cosmologists in Kyoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is this "Grand Master"\Nof the Octobrist Organization?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Four-Eyed Boobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Olminu! That's not\Neven close to my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain to me the situation \Nwith the Long Ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You mean now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can imagine most of it \Nmyself, so do it briefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Those people are called Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decades ago, the humans attacked,\Ndefeated, and subjugated them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, they live their lives as serfs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. What kind of creatures are Elves?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... they have a long life expectancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I heard that they were naturally proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyohisa, tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Stand next to me and say what I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be the one to\Nspeak up in a situation like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toyo, tell them what you told me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them like this... Then, like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are underhanded.\NNo wonder you were betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a disgrace to your forefathers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not bring humiliation \Nto your children?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wish to have your own state?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you grovel and die with regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will you run and die dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way will you choose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why wouldn't we be ashamed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't we want our country back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would we be okay with...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,being slaves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's go get your state back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oh, I like his defiant look...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me a bit of...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you make me the commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've taken on the role, Nobunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather be a figure who pulls\Nthe strings behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son died in Nijou Palace!\NHe was killed by Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Shimazu Toyohisa.\NI am not Oda Nobutada!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I know that, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't resemble him at all,\Nyou idiot. That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my father were still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he would be around that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:55.01,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mutter mutter mutter"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iehisa is long dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Oda Nobunaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you just say, you jackass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna fight, punk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hyaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? They started fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop them!\N--Stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... This brings back memories...\NBrotherly fights...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the ten brothers,\Nare going to side with the Taira clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoichi, you are on the \NGenjis' side, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were eleven of us. It was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:41.27,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Nasu Clan"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you use a bow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lord's forces could be\Napproaching as you speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no time for fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Shara, son of the village\Nelder who was killed by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for looking after my brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! So this is your big brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say, "They could be approaching."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they are closing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.53,0:17:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those soldiers whom you killed\Ndidn't return from patrol duties,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they began to assemble\Nthe troops, which will take...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would guess four days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are well equipped, so maybe sooner.\NIt'll probably take three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shimazus could do that by the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is because your clan \Nis a bunch of freaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn belligerent tribe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Nlikely the day after tomorrow is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the day your village ceases to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:18:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... lend us your strength!\NWe have never taken up arms to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.56,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were only children when our country\Nwas destroyed forty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our fathers and brothers who fought\Nin the battle were all killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.43,0:18:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We hardly know how to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just say something strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? I'm 106 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't joke around. You could be\Nexecuted if you were in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two. How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirty-nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thirty-six.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you explain that, Boobienu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:53.07,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Honk honk"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Olminu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.38,0:18:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any intention\Nof remembering my name, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't grab my boobs,\Nyou perverted old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Elves are expected to live long lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.61,0:18:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their life expectancy is about five\Nto six times greater than humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their rate of maturation is slow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's wrong?\N--What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are older...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This area used to be Elven land
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until Orte, the human kingdom\Nin the East, destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.84,0:19:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orte also conquered the states\Nof the Dwarfs and the Hobbits
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and subjugated them,\Nforcing them to be serfs and miners.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Orte then\Nproclaimed their state to be an empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and enforced the system of occupation,\Nsetting a doctrine of human supremacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this so-called Orte still expanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are currently engaged in\Nbattles all around the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, their battle fronts\Nhave reached equilibrium.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's expected. Conquering a state\Nis like spinning a burning wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we claim a state,\Nwe only have two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either utterly destroy it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or hand over everything as you\Nwould to pacify a crying princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orte forty years ago would've been
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a major ally in the fight \Nagainst the Black King,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.93,0:20:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but present-day Orte is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.34,0:20:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't do either, leaving the\Ngrudges of the occupied to fester.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, it has been forty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was as if they started\Na wildfire in a withered field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody and his brother\Nis filled with resentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That explains why those \Nfools acted recklessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Orte doesn't teach them a lesson,\Nthey will become uncontrollable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why Orte will definitely come to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,slaughter everyone as a warning to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do now, Toyohisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As commander, what are\Nyou going to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.54,0:20:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the tactics of\Nthe Shimazu clan, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going to let them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.40,0:21:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it overkill, dispatching 200 troops\Nto destroy one Elven village?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Aram and his \Npatrol were all killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way those Elves have the guts to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.04,0:21:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were rumors that they\Nwere killed by the Drifters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drifters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.92,0:21:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, there were just \Na few of them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the Drifters... really that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nobody here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place is completely empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.20,0:21:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they disappear to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to kill all of them tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take everyone's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Boobienu Orgaization"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Power of Shit"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.72,0:23:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Monkey Yell"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 5\NBring Back Love"